    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✤故事✤</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158290/extras/0dfc568f9f5d9979626105a9c548c4d2.avif?t=1762826800\" width=600 height=284 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女战士蕾贝卡是这座边境小村内最强的战士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蕾贝卡不只剑术强大，心地也十分善良，在村里担当着类似村庄守护者的角色，深受村民们信赖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但某天，蕾贝卡的村庄被盗贼团袭击了。蕾贝卡虽然勇敢应战，但村民们还是几乎都被掳走了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她的单相思对象竹藏也不例外。于是蕾贝卡踏上了旅程，誓言一定要打倒盗贼团，拯救村民们。<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在崭新的大陆上，蕾贝卡获得了魔剑。而这把魔剑将会大幅改变她的命运……！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当盗贼团被打倒，蕾贝卡成功夺回心上人的那一刻，村里最强的女战士究竟会迎来怎样的结局？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✤游戏内容✤</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158290/extras/bfbcc4c0b6d7e55b2ccfdc6bc6907f26.avif?t=1762826800\" width=600 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲将港口城镇作为据点前往攻略各个地图吧！根据攻略进度，能够前往的地方也会变多。<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158290/extras/8c980f8465b26fa93e38f229f70a2a92.avif?t=1762826800\" width=600 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲可以跟各式各样的敌人战斗，赚取经验值后可以提升等级。<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158290/extras/889e1ec4116f0af78ea1f0101bd263d3.avif?t=1762826800\" width=600 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲地图上会掉落各式各样的素材，可以将这些素材拿去换钱。<br> </p>",
